reviewText: A collection of old and mediocre movies.  I would not recormmend.
Great set of movies for the  price.
Take note, some serious drama. No teen bs here.specifically At Close Range.  it'll pull you in, possibly disturb you , but ultimately they're all well done and very worth a look.
Don't buy this.  It doesn't upconvert so you are left with a small film surrounded by black screen.  Perfect example of why you should never shop late at night.
